{
  "tailwindText": "Introducing Oatmeal\nOur new multi-theme marketing site kit\nUI Blocks\nTemplates\nUI Kit\nSign in\nGet full access\nUI Blocks\nApplication UI\nHeadings\nSection Headings\n\nSection heading examples for Tailwind CSS, designed and built by the creators of the framework.\n\nSimple\n\nPreview\n\nGet the code →\nWith description\n\nPreview\n\nGet the code →\nWith actions\n\nPreview\n\nGet the code →\nWith action\n\nPreview\n\nGet the code →\nWith input group\n\nPreview\n\nGet the code →\nWith tabs\n\nPreview\n\nGet the code →\nWith actions and tabs\n\nPreview\n\nGet the code →\nWith inline tabs\n\nPreview\n\nGet the code →\nWith label\n\nPreview\n\nGet the code →\nWith badge and dropdown\n\nPreview\n\nGet the code →\nMarketing\nHero Sections\nFeature Sections\nPricing Sections\nHeader Sections\nNewsletter Sections\nTestimonials\nTeam Sections\nContent Sections\nLogo Clouds\nFAQs\nFooters\nHeaders\nFlyout Menus\nBanners\nBrowse all →\nApplication UI\nTables\nFeeds\nForm Layouts\nSelect Menus\nRadio Groups\nCheckboxes\nComboboxes\nNavbars\nPagination\nSidebar Navigation\nCommand Palettes\nModals\nDropdowns\nButtons\nBrowse all →\nEcommerce\nProduct Overviews\nProduct Lists\nCategory Previews\nShopping Carts\nCategory Filters\nProduct Quickviews\nProduct Features\nStore Navigation\nPromo Sections\nCheckout Forms\nReviews\nOrder Summaries\nOrder History\nIncentives\nBrowse all →\nTemplates & UI Kits\nCatalyst UI Kit\nPersonal Website Template\nLanding Page Template\nAPI Reference Template\nChangelog Template\nInfo Product Template\nAgency Template\nPodcast Template\nApp Marketing Template\nDocumentation Template\nConference Template\nBrowse all →\n\n© 2026 Tailwind Labs Inc. All rights reserved.\n\nPrivacy policy\nChangelog",
  "localText": "UI Dictionary\n\nCtrl F\nUI Blocks\nTemplates\nUI Kit\nSign in\nGet full access\nMarketing\nApplication UI\nEcommerce\nDocumentation\nAPPLICATION SHELLS\nStacked Layouts\nSidebar Layouts\nMulti-Column Layouts\nHEADINGS\nPage Headings\nCard Headings\nSection Headings\nDATA DISPLAY\nDescription Lists\nStats\nCalendars\nLISTS\nStacked Lists\nTables\nGrid Lists\nFeeds\nFORMS\nForm Layouts\nInput Groups\nSelect Menus\nSign-in and Registration\nTextareas\nRadio Groups\nCheckboxes\nToggles\nAction Panels\nComboboxes\nFEEDBACK\nAlerts\nEmpty States\nNAVIGATION\nNavbars\nPagination\nTabs\nVertical Navigation\nSidebar Navigation\nBreadcrumbs\nProgress Bars\nCommand Palettes\nOVERLAYS\nModal Dialogs\nDrawers\nNotifications\nELEMENTS\nAvatars\nBadges\nDropdowns\nButtons\nButton Groups\nLAYOUT\nContainers\nCards\nList containers\nMedia Objects\nDividers\nPAGE EXAMPLES\nHome Screens\nDetail Screens\nSettings Screens\n\nPLUS / UI BLOCKS / APPLICATION UI / HEADINGS / SECTION HEADINGS\n\nSection Headings\n\n설정, 상세, 대시보드 안에서 정보 묶음을 구분하는 제목 패턴입니다.\n\nTailwind Plus처럼 각 leaf의 첫 예제는 Preview와 Code를 함께 제공하고, 이후 예제는 Preview와 잠금 code CTA로 구분합니다. 우리 예시는 실제 화면 맥락에 맞춘 설명, tags, interaction feedback을 함께 보여줍니다.\n\nON THIS PAGE\n\n10 examples\nSimple\nWith description\nWith actions\nWith action\nWith input group\nWith tabs\nWith actions and tabs\nWith inline tabs\nWith label\nSimple\nEXAMPLE 01\n\nTailwind의 section heading 예시 이름과 개수를 맞춘 섹션 제목 변형입니다.\n\nsection heading\ntabs\nactions\nPreview\nCode\nHTML\nReact\nVue\nJob Postings\nWith description\nEXAMPLE 02\n\nTailwind의 section heading 예시 이름과 개수를 맞춘 섹션 제목 변형입니다.\n\nsection heading\ntabs\nactions\nPreview\nGet the code →\nJob Postings\n\nWorkcation is a sample hiring workspace where teams review roles, candidates, and workflow status.\n\nWith actions\nEXAMPLE 03\n\nTailwind의 section heading 예시 이름과 개수를 맞춘 섹션 제목 변형입니다.\n\nsection heading\ntabs\nactions\nPreview\nGet the code →\nJob Postings\nShare\nCreate\nWith action\nEXAMPLE 04\n\nTailwind의 section heading 예시 이름과 개수를 맞춘 섹션 제목 변형입니다.\n\nsection heading\ntabs\nactions\nPreview\nGet the code →\nJob Postings\nCreate new job\nWith input group\nEXAMPLE 05\n\nTailwind의 section heading 예시 이름과 개수를 맞춘 섹션 제목 변형입니다.\n\nsection heading\ntabs\nactions\nPreview\nGet the code →\nJob Postings\nSearch candidates\nSort\nWith tabs\nEXAMPLE 06\n\nTailwind의 section heading 예시 이름과 개수를 맞춘 섹션 제목 변형입니다.\n\nsection heading\ntabs\nactions\nPreview\nGet the code →\nCandidates\nApplied\nPhone Screening\nInterview\nOffer\nHired\n\nShowing Interview\n\nWith actions and tabs\nEXAMPLE 07\n\nTailwind의 section heading 예시 이름과 개수를 맞춘 섹션 제목 변형입니다.\n\nsection heading\ntabs\nactions\nPreview\nGet the code →\nCandidates\nApplied\nPhone Screening\nInterview\nOffer\nHired\n\nShowing Interview\n\nShare\nCreate\nWith inline tabs\nEXAMPLE 08\n\nTailwind의 section heading 예시 이름과 개수를 맞춘 섹션 제목 변형입니다.\n\nsection heading\ntabs\nactions\nPreview\nGet the code →\nIssues\nOpen\nClosed\n\nShowing Open\n\nWith label\nEXAMPLE 09\n\nTailwind의 section heading 예시 이름과 개수를 맞춘 섹션 제목 변형입니다.\n\nsection heading\ntabs\nactions\nPreview\nGet the code →\nJob Postings\nin Engineering\nWith badge and dropdown\nEXAMPLE 10\n\nTailwind의 section heading 예시 이름과 개수를 맞춘 섹션 제목 변형입니다.\n\nsection heading\ntabs\nactions\nPreview\nGet the code →\nFull-Stack Developer\n\nCheckout and Payments Team\n\nOpen\n...",
